{"tid":2492101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"每日4罐   連飲2年能量飲品　21歲男大學生體重急劇下跌  心臟衰竭險喪命","createTime":"2021-04-16T23:36:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T00:58:34.000Z","uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0182f15e2838d014bc5b2c977b96566eea60b2b8","tid":2492101,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:36:23.000Z","msg":"市面上各種「機能飲料」，標榜可提神增強體力，眼用時仍須注意切勿過量。英國一名21歲的男大學生，過去2年間每天喝4罐500毫升的機能飲料，結果體重狂掉呼吸急促，最後竟然心臟衰竭進了加護病房！<br />\n<br />\n最新一期《英國醫學期刊》(BMJ，British Medical Journal)刊載了這個案例。位於倫敦的英國國民保健署基金會立蓋伊與聖托馬斯醫院(Guy&rsquo;s and St Thomas&rsquo; NHS Foundation Trust)的醫師表示，這是一起嚴重的雙心室心臟衰竭(biventricular heart failure)個案，很可能與這名21歲患者長期過量飲用能量飲料有關。<br />\n<br />\n醫師表示，這名21歲男大生並無其他病史，但<strong><span class=\"red\">在過去2年間，每天飲用4罐、每罐500毫升的能量飲料，根據標示，每一罐含有至少160毫克的咖啡因，每天咖啡因的攝入量遠高於一般成年人建議的每天200至300毫克。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n這名男大生在發病前4個月，體重開始急遽下降，且經常呼吸困難，後來到醫院檢查時已經出現心臟衰竭與腎衰竭的症狀，立刻被送入加護病房治療，<strong><span class=\"red\">「我們相信，過量攝入機能飲料引發的心臟毒性(cardiotoxicity)是最大的可能」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n姓名並未公開的男大生最後在醫院住了58天，醫療團隊一度評估他是否需要進行器官移植保命。康復後的男大生表示：「<strong><span class=\"red\">我每天喝4罐機量飲料，有時會感到心悸，這干擾了我日常工作和學習的專注力；但我沒喝機能飲料時，又會感到嚴重的偏頭痛，甚至會限制我日常的休閒活動，例如去公園或散步</span></strong>」，「後來我被送進加護病房，這段時間讓我非常痛苦」，「我認為大眾應該對於這類飲料的成分、含量與影響有更多的認識」，「機能飲料的包裝上應該要有清楚的警告標示，就像香菸包裝上的警告標示一樣，說明飲用這飲料的潛在危險」。（於慶中／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"933b3fcdc3235b05dcd531e1293ad891629f64cc","tid":2492101,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:39:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210417/TKCMLPW6FFBOZBQSWQCQZWJJ44/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210417%2FTKCMLPW6FFBOZBQSWQCQZWJJ44%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL2yprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=154f349c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210417%2FTKCMLPW6FFBOZBQSWQCQZWJJ44%2F&h=376546ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210417/TKCMLPW6FFBOZBQSWQCQZWJJ44/</a>"},{"pid":"69e2ba5d66eb988dca8945139246fe789e953588","tid":2492101,"uid":3967,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:41:59.000Z","msg":"gym友日日飲"},{"pid":"d311e4b2ab51108b244e6524ac882052dcf78f9d","tid":2492101,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"69e2ba5d66eb988dca8945139246fe789e953588","tid":2492101,"uid":3967,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:41:59.000Z","msg":"gym友日日飲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:44:28.000Z","msg":"飲幾多罐先得架"},{"pid":"94adbce3de7fb4143be178fe86ee2f6680ff61fc","tid":2492101,"uid":308251,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:44:31.000Z","msg":"戇尻，啲能量飲品寫到明每日最多兩罐，大嘅就每日一罐，好明顯係用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25434fc96ecce35d65b6edd9b76167c8f3844a04","tid":2492101,"uid":243756,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:48:50.000Z","msg":"飲就心悸<br />\n唔飲就嚴重偏頭痛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係應該一早去醫頭痛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/door.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/door.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/door.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7537da4a24e01ad6f2a9e4d3f38bb1fdb51f59f7","tid":2492101,"uid":204533,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"25434fc96ecce35d65b6edd9b76167c8f3844a04","tid":2492101,"uid":243756,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T23:48:50.000Z","msg":"飲就心悸<br />\n唔飲就嚴重偏頭痛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad